# Rockbox integration (2026-07-19 Solar-only policy)

- **Do not install** `org.rockbox` via APK platform prep, OTA companion, or first-boot self-heal.
- **Launch-if-present** is fine (switch scripts / `am start` when the package already exists).
- **Y1 ROM** may still bake Rockbox for now; **Y2** default ROM strips Rockbox/JJ.
- When Rockbox *is* present, keep Xposed hooks (IME/compat) and lib sync (`RockboxLibSync` → `y1/` / `/system/etc/solar` scripts) minimal and well-commented.
- Storage path patches (Y2 `sdcard1` vs Y1 `sdcard0`) stay minimally invasive per ponytail; apply in adb smoke, local build, and CI when touching Rockbox ROM paths.